SHIFT4 PAYMENTS
Merchant Statement Stuffing Program
•	During the week of October 9, 2017, Shift4 will be launching a
statement stuffer program targeting all CardConnect merchants.
•	These stuffers will be placed in every merchant statement, ensuring
100% of the CardConnect base receives our message.
•	These stuffers will highlight the CardConnect/First Data
breaches, the "misleading" PCI program and all of the hidden fees
charged to their merchants.
•	They, also, will include a call to-action for merchants to call a special
toll-free number that will be dedicated to this program.
•	All calls will be routed directly to Sales Ops so they can collect as
much information as possible and forward to the appropriate rep.
•	We expect this to generate significant leads, as well as damage
CardConnect/First Data's reputations in the marketplace.
